# Privacy Policy for Walmart Offer Activator

**Effective Date:** February 10, 2026

## 1. Introduction
Walmart Offer Activator ("the Extension") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains our practices regarding data collection and usage.

## 2. No Data Collection
**We do not collect, store, or transmit any user data.**[cite: 5, 6]. The extension is designed to operate entirely within your browser without sending any information to external servers or third parties.

## 3. Extension Permissions and Usage
The Extension requires specific permissions to function correctly, which are used solely for the following purposes:
* **Host Permission (Walmart.com):** Used exclusively to identify and activate available offers on the Walmart website.
* **Scripting/activeTab:** Used only to interact with the elements on the Walmart page to automate the offer activation process.

## 4. Data Security
Since no data is collected or transmitted, there is no risk of your personal information being compromised through the use of this extension.

## 5. Changes to This Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

## 6. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: **admin@ost4p.com**[cite: 1].
